  Last Modified: 2025-12-17 14:28:45
  
  Usage:
    <%%- include('partials/cet-apps-info-modal') %%>
  
  Modal Trigger:
    - Activated by clicking the info button on the CET Apps View page
    - Button selector: data-bs-target="#cetAppsInfoModal"
  
  Dependencies:
    - Bootstrap 5.x (modal, buttons, alerts, badges)
    - Bootstrap Icons (bi-* classes for application indicators)
    - info-modal-resources.ejs (included partial for resource links)
  
  Sections Covered:
    - Overview of CET Applications registry
    - Application configuration details
    - Column descriptions (iGate App, CET App, Server, Database, etc.)
