<div class="modal fade" id="cetAppsInfoModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="cetAppsInfoModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-scrollable">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header bg-primary text-white">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="cetAppsInfoModalLabel">
          <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>About CET Applications
        </h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <h6 class="text-primary mb-3"><i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line me-2"></i>Overview</h6>
        <p>
          The <strong>CET Applications</strong> page serves as a comprehensive configuration registry for all CET (Central Engine Technology) applications in your environment. This centralized reference provides essential technical details needed to manage, troubleshoot, and access each CET application.
        </p>
        <p>
          Use this page to quickly find server locations, database connections, port configurations, and support resources for any CET application in your infrastructure.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-4">

        <h6 class="text-primary mb-3"><i class="bi bi-speedometer2 me-2"></i>Key Metrics</h6>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
              <i class="bi bi-hdd-stack text-primary me-2 fs-5"></i>
              <div>
                <strong>Total Applications</strong>
                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Total number of applications registered in the CET configuration registry</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
              <i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2 fs-5"></i>
              <div>
                <strong>Active</strong>
                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Number of applications currently in active status and available for use</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
              <i class="bi bi-server text-info me-2 fs-5"></i>
              <div>
                <strong>SQL Servers</strong>
                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Count of distinct SQL Server instances configured across all applications</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
              <i class="bi bi-building text-secondary me-2 fs-5"></i>
              <div>
                <strong>iGate Apps</strong>
                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Number of applications integrated with iGate enterprise systems</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-4">

        <h6 class="text-primary mb-3"><i class="bi bi-table me-2"></i>Column Descriptions</h6>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12">
            <div class="table-responsive">
              <table class="table table-sm table-bordered">
                <thead class="table-light">
                  <tr>
                    <th class="modal-col-25">Column</th>
                    <th class="modal-col-75">Description</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong><i class="bi bi-building text-primary me-1"></i>iGate App</strong></td>
                    <td>The iGate application name that hosts or manages this CET application. Multiple CET apps may be associated with a single iGate application.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong><i class="bi bi-gear-wide-connected text-primary me-1"></i>CET APP</strong></td>
                    <td>The unique name or identifier for the specific CET application. This is the primary identifier used throughout the system.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong><i class="bi bi-server text-primary me-1"></i>SQL Server</strong></td>
                    <td>The SQL Server instance where this CET application's database is hosted. Used for database connectivity and troubleshooting.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong><i class="bi bi-database text-primary me-1"></i>Database</strong></td>
                    <td>The specific database name used by this CET application. Contains the application's data, queues, and processing tables.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong><i class="bi bi-file-text text-primary me-1"></i>Description</strong></td>
                    <td>A brief description of what the CET application does, its purpose, or the business process it supports.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong><i class="bi bi-link-45deg text-primary me-1"></i>Support Link</strong></td>
                    <td>A clickable link to additional documentation, support pages, or configuration details for this application. Opens in a new tab.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong><i class="bi bi-circle-fill text-success me-1"></i>Status</strong></td>
                    <td>Current operational status of the application. Typically shows "Active" (green) for running applications or "Inactive" for disabled ones.</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-4">

        <h6 class="text-primary mb-3"><i class="bi bi-search me-2"></i>Features</h6>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-1"></i> <strong>Search & Filter:</strong> Quickly find applications by name, server, database, or status</li>
          <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-1"></i> <strong>Sortable Columns:</strong> Click any column header to sort data alphabetically or by status</li>
          <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-1"></i> <strong>Export Options:</strong> Export the registry to CSV or Excel for documentation</li>
          <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-1"></i> <strong>External Links:</strong> Click support links to access detailed documentation in a new tab</li>
          <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-1"></i> <strong>Live Summary Cards:</strong> Summary metrics update dynamically as you filter the table</li>
          <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-1"></i> <strong>Keyboard Navigation:</strong> Full keyboard accessibility support for efficient browsing</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-4">

        <h6 class="text-primary mb-3"><i class="bi bi-lightbulb me-2"></i>Quick Tips</h6>
        <div class="alert alert-info mb-2">
          <strong><i class="bi bi-search me-1"></i>Use the search box</strong> to quickly locate applications by any column value
        </div>
        <div class="alert alert-success mb-2">
          <strong><i class="bi bi-link-45deg me-1"></i>Click support links</strong> to access detailed technical documentation and configuration guides
        </div>
        <div class="alert alert-warning mb-0">
          <strong><i class="bi bi-funnel me-1"></i>Apply filters</strong> to view applications by server, database, or status for targeted analysis
        </div>

        <hr class="my-4">

        <!-- Resources Section -->
        <%- include('info-modal-resources', {
          collapseId: 'cetAppsResourcesCollapse'
        }) %>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
